 href=\"https://news.efinancialcareers.com/ie-en/313226/the-top-employers-of-cfas-globally-in-2018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.efinancialcareers.com%2Fie-en%2F313226%2Fthe-top-employers-of-cfas-globally-in-2018&d=sX8bL84bYpOGpKt1KXoOYwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=c8be40d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.efinancialcareers.com/ie-en/313226/the-top-employers-of-cfas-globally-in-2018</a><br />\n<br />\nJPM, UBS, RBC, BAML, HSBC, MS, Citi, Blackrock, CS<br />\n<br />\nSome interesting trends emerge when looking at the data across a four-year stretch. While the pool of employed CFAs will likely continue to grow &ndash; more people earn their charter each year, likely outpacing the number of CFAs who retire or become unemployed &ndash; it&rsquo;s noteworthy that not one of the companies in the list saw a dip in the number of CFAs they employ during any of the four years. That&rsquo;s particularly impressive considering nine out of the 10 firms are large banks that have generally trimmed staff since 2015.<br />\n<br />\nWhen looking at specific firms, J.P. Morgan stands out &ndash; and not just because they employ more CFAs than any other company. They&rsquo;ve also increased their CFA pool by 26% over the last four years, representing the biggest increase among all top 10 firms.<br />\n<br />\nBut perhaps more illuminating is the fact that BlackRock, an investment firm with around 14,000 workers, employs over 1,100 CFAs &ndash; up roughly 23% compared to 2015. Nearly 8% of all BlackRock employees have their CFA, according to the figures. If you want to work at BlackRock, now is a good time. The fund is currently hiring while paying better than in years past. Having your CFA certainly won&rsquo;t hurt your chances."},{"pid":"d34ae518ebd54c894310ea883cf008c0dc143c29","tid":701701,"uid":178572,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T15:39:35.000Z","msg":"補充返:<br />\n考到=/=大機會入到大行<br />\n大部份人係入左先去考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65909a8cd7a1184eeb8fce440e97abdfaad5959b","tid":701701,"uid":58998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T15:42:20.000Z","msg":"Level 1係無用，因為pass一份卷根本無任何qualification<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且level1個難度本身都未難過大學finance嘅課程"},{"pid":"2ef4678af0e268993c18001571bd302b9f796e29","tid":701701,"uid":58998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d34ae518ebd54c894310ea883cf008c0dc143c29","tid":701701,"uid":178572,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T15:39:35.000Z","msg":"補充返:<br />\n考到=/=大機會入到大行<br />\n大部份人係入左先去考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T15:43:01.000Z","msg":"入咗去先考有得reimburse <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成皮嘢喎"},{"pid":"8e54de1385a7a709c72f31592772a50406ae1773","tid":701701,"uid":178572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ef4678af0e268993c18001571bd302b9f796e29","tid":701701,"uid":58998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d34ae518ebd54c894310ea883cf008c0dc143c29","tid":701701,"uid":178572,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T15:39:35.000Z","msg":"補充返:<br />\n考到=/=大機會入到大行<br />\n大部份人係入左先去考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T15:43:01.000Z","msg":"入咗去先考有得reimburse <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成皮嘢喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T15:53:00.000Z","msg":"當然啦，考試費有得claim，又可以放幾日study leave<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大把人考"}]}